<p>Post-1991 trickle down effect of Indian economy was dismantled.</p>
<p>Govt Liberalised and privatised making market the king but also provided adequate safeguards</p>
<p>Economic survey 2021 highlights growth to reduce poverty = govt. get more tax hence more welfare + more resources with the poor (income up) via inclusive growth</p>
